Blackstar to Sell a 54% Stake in Ferro Industrial Products for $28 Million

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-08-15T05:07:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-15/blackstar-to-sell-54-stake-in-ferro-industrial-products-for-28-million.html
Blackstar Group SE agreed to sell
its 54 percent stake in Ferro Industrial Products Ltd. for 200
million rand, the company said in a statement published today in
the Johannesburg-based Business Day newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  